name: ChronicPainConditions
title: Chronic Pain Conditions
description: This value set may undergo changes until the HL7 Multiple Chronic Care FHIR IG is formally published in 2024.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains diagnoses or problem terms representing that chronic pain exists.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this set of values is to identify patients who have chronic pain diagnoses or problems documented in a clinical record.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes chronic pain encoded terms.),(Exclusion Criteria: Encoded terms not representative of chronic pain. Does not include specific conditions associated with chronic pain.)
